<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-heading-small-font-size">How We Can Help You</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"fontSize":"medium"} -->
<p class="has-medium-font-size">After a UK document has received an apostille, it will be recognized in the other countries that have signed the Hague Apostille Convention (the majority of countries internationally).</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"fontSize":"medium"} -->
<p class="has-medium-font-size">Contact us for a free consultation – phone us toll-free at&nbsp;<a href="tel:1-888-433-1011">1-888-433-1011</a>&nbsp;or send us a quick&nbsp;<a href="https://idocs.local/get-in-touch/">online enquiry</a>. We’ll explain the process to you, answer your questions, and discuss your options.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div>
